data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Home with a 3 Car Garage, Full rear Fenced yard overlooking a serene pond.  Two Story Vaulted Great Room with large Loft. Main Floor Master Suite.  Good sized bedrooms two and three.  In addition to a 17 x 12 Finished attic area for extra storage.  All appliances are included, including the washer & dryer! Oversized concrete patio for entertaining with 220 outlet for a hot tub.  You will enjoy the tranquil setting in the back yard.  All this plus the three car garage for all your storage and third car needs. Rounding out the outside amenities there is a community pool & beautiful pond behind the home where you can enjoy some fishing!
